                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17821016-54-defend585 t17821016-54-punish287"></join>
               confined to hard labour, for six months in the house of correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury, before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
